ptured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Raw text splits by paragraph, punctuation, then characters (TRANSLATION_MAX_CHUNK_CHARS=5000). Chunks translated in parallel by ThreadPoolExecutor; results joined by original index."}, {"id": "concept_glossary_extraction", "label": "Automatic glossary extraction post-translation", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "PROJECT_SPEC.md", "source_location": "section 2", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "After translating a chapter, an extra LLM call extracts new glossary terms if AUTO_EXTRACT_GLOSSARY=true. Exceptions during extraction are silently swallowed."}, {"id": "concept_5_summary_context", "label": "5-summary context window for next chapter", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "PROJECT_SPEC.md", "source_location": "section 9", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Up to 5 most recent ChapterSummary rows selected by creation ID are passed as context when translating the next chapter, preserving narrative continuity."}, {"id": "concept_three_view_reader", "label": "Three-view reader (raw/vi/both)", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "PROJECT_SPEC.md", "source_location": "section 12", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "GET /chapters/{id}?view=raw|vi|both with default vi. Server-rendered tabs, parallel two-column on desktop for view=both."}, {"id": "concept_db_overrides_env", "label": "DB ProviderSetting overrides .env fallback", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "PROJECT_SPEC.md", "source_location": "section 5", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "A ProviderSetting DB row overrides .env configuration for that provider; clearing the row reverts to env fallback."}, {"id": "concept_in_memory_thread_registry", "label": "In-memory thread registry (tech debt: